{
  "texts": [
    "Mehrabi et al. [93] test their FLIRT framework to analyze text-to-image models like Stable Diffusion.",
    "Still other researchers perform red-teaming of LLMs for specific end-uses.",
    "Lewis & White [84] red-team an LLM for potential future use as a component of a virtual museum tourguide, and He et al. [65] evaluate the dangers of using LLMs as part of scientific research.",
    "In light of the many documented ways generative AI models can be utilized for malicious use, researchers have also studied ways in which they can be defended.",
    "Both Sun et al. [148] and Wang et al."
  ]
}